/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e65f6e8a82493b7f190759a41f72c7dc7718027","tid":324652,"uid":101253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做運動 keep fit 增加多啲自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最近開始緊每日練core muscle<br />\n但運動真係可以增加多啲自信？</blockquote><br />\n會令你到自己身材有自信"},{"pid":"3bf5eaf8fc74d6dff41bcb9b3087ba94f00c3e33","tid":324652,"uid":55770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:14:52.000Z","msg":"你咁樣另一半仲大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafdf990eee75cc243704671c32bdc5cc3decdb9","tid":324652,"uid":127610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"某程度同你成長環境好大關係<br />\n你應該係好想獲得人地認同的人<br />\n要靠身邊的人肯定先有存在感<br />\n你對自己要求都好高<br />\n<br />\n想了解你自己更多，我可以同你慢慢傾<br />\n由你細個開始"},{"pid":"1a185a036d8c23fe800bd856eec9b2e30c582f4a","tid":324652,"uid":86334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>某程度同你成長環境好大關係<br />\n你應該係好想獲得人地認同的人<br />\n要靠身邊的人肯定先有存在感<br />\n你對自己要求都好高<br />\n<br />\n想了解你自己更多，我可以同你慢慢傾<br />\n由你細個開始</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗應該係...<br />\n加我tg<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Shu00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FShu00&d=lkS6DTQKXjoRIIxnjKOnfTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a4e12466\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Shu00</a>"},{"pid":"ba46914fe14ecd32eaac3d9745445f0171cad021","tid":324652,"uid":128410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"同你一模一樣<br />\n我成日會數我身上面覺得唔滿意嘅地方 係有四十幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n明明身邊嘅人都覺得我Ok靚女 但係我會覺得自己係一個缺憾 父母所有唔好嘅野都遺傳晒比我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/